{"tid":2127482,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人真係好唔鍾意玩遊戲？","createTime":"2020-07-27T10:48:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T12:34:45.000Z","uid":63392,"like":7,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"71a74ee517da7bb66e4ce352990a9d23a2241787","tid":2127482,"uid":63392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:48:30.000Z","msg":"唔鍾意玩遊戲呢樣嘢真係由細已經表現出嚟<br />\n記得5、6歲左右 喺朋友仔生日會玩冚棉胎 <br />\n冚棉胎好考反應 我又鋪鋪都輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩到最尾喺全部人面前喊𠹌咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成長過程都唔特別鍾意玩video game/ card game/ board game/ 麻雀<br />\n亦唔會走去研究點玩<br />\n咩勁舞團跑online都冇興趣<br />\n鍾意玩嘅得尼奧寵物同忍豆風雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n數理又由細到大都特別差<br />\n上網做嗰啲睇圖形嗰啲iq test<br />\n又完全睇唔明<br />\n<br />\n到大咗入大學 開始要玩房game 酒game<br />\n我又極唔在行<br />\n狼人又唔識玩 猜枚又勁廢 <br />\n啤牌又永遠唔識分嗰啲組合（係，我連啲組合名都up唔出 咩乎佬嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n學打麻雀又學極都要諗勁耐<br />\n但身邊嘅人就玩到勁行在咁<br />\n覺得好羨慕<br />\n<br />\n有冇人都係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次一到玩遊戲就真係覺得好唔自在<br />\n係咪我智商有問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b6cec017510afb550426dbe7c1870eeea85fde","tid":2127482,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:49:03.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"f63e6f0f8a94ae96c0a293219d7a3e6cc463687f","tid":2127482,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:49:13.000Z","msg":"唔係"},{"pid":"6cbfacf60d94e9a08b18c7a13e07bf2a5ba0a754","tid":2127482,"uid":209097,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:49:19.000Z","msg":"其實係智商有問題 check下比較好"},{"pid":"778f533a31ffe44dddf9b608d5073b14cd02adb4","tid":2127482,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:49:29.000Z","msg":"可能係"},{"pid":"a52108e81ad05f577c37506702